item.title: CVE-2019-1003084|2024-08-05T03:07:18.090Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20zephyr%20enterprise%20test%20management%20plugin
item.description: A cross-site request forgery vulnerability in Jenkins Zephyr Enterprise Test Management Plugin in the ZeeDescriptor#doTestConnection form validation method allows attackers to initiate a connection to an attacker-specified server.

item.title: CVE-2019-1003085|2024-08-05T03:07:18.272Z -- jenkins%20project -- jenkins%20zephyr%20enterprise%20test%20management%20plugin
item.description: A missing permission check in Jenkins Zephyr Enterprise Test Management Plugin in the ZeeDescriptor#doTestConnection form validation method allows attackers with Overall/Read permission to initiate a connection to an attacker-specified server.
